headline: PSEG (PEG) Q1 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: PSEG (PEG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.05% and 12.98%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
